        <p style="centeredText"><![CDATA[$\begin{matrix}C-D&=&\begin{bmatrix}2-(-3)&5-5&1-5\\[6pt]3-8&7-(-6)&8-4\end{bmatrix}\\[20pt]&=&\begin{bmatrix}5&0&-4\\[6pt]-5&13&4\end{bmatrix}\hspace{2.2cm}\end{matrix}$]]></p>
      </stack>
